      "instruction": "<p>Top and tail the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into quarters lengthways, then cut into batons</p>\n<p>Deseed the <strong>red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p>\n<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>ginger</strong></p>",
